title: Domestic Violence
description: I offer legal representation by an attorney in the defense of domestic violence charges. The representation includes court hearings, injunction hearings, restraining orders, and disposition where the member is a defendant.

title: Documents Preparation
description: When entering into a legal contract or finalizing legal documents, having the assistance of an attorney with your best interest in mind can be the difference between a successful resolution and an unfavorable outcome. I assist with the creation or review of personal legal documents such as demand letters, deeds, promissory notes, bills of sale, and many more common legal documents.

title: Personal Injury
description: When dealing with a case of personal injury or wrongful death, it is important you have an attorney on your side who can fight for you and your family. This coverage includes representation by an attorney based on a contingency fee agreement for auto accidents, medical malpractice, and similar causes of action.

title: Traffic Violations
description: Traffic violations occur when drivers defy laws put in place to ensure the safety of everyone on the roads. Considering the fact that over 90% of all Americans over age 16 are licensed to drive a vehicle, traffic violations are very common.

title: Identity Theft
description: With identity crimes at an all-time high, protecting yourself and your family against identity theft is critical to ensuring your general and financial safety. In order to help our members combat the financial and emotional damage done by these thefts, an Identity Restoration Program is included in our plans.

title: Marital and Family
description: When it comes to your family, you're dedicated to their protection and well-being. I understand how important legal matters relating to your family are. Our coverage regarding family relationships includes matters such as divorce, child support, and child custody. Legal help also includes changing and/or enforcing existing arrangements set by the court.
